data.description: VA Assumable rate 2.875% IMMACULATE two-story home is located in a sought-after neighborhood. Heavy Duty Shingles Roof replaced 2022, Spray Foam Insulation, Gas Cooking! This home boasts over 2800 sq ft of elegant living space and features 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, a separate dining area, media room, game room, and impressive high ceilings. The exterior is adorned with stone and stucco on three sides, complemented by an 8ft front door. Enjoy the spacious covered patio at the back, tasteful interior paint, and exquisite tile flooring in most parts of the home, enhanced by numerous LED recessed lights and upgraded fixtures. The master bedroom is a true retreat with a lovely bay window and an en-suite bathroom complete with a garden tub and walk-in shower. The luxurious kitchen is equipped with a large island, refined granite countertops, custom white cabinets, a built-in office space, and generously sized secondary bedrooms. The private backyard is enclosed with a stone fence at the rear. Come and experience this stunning home for yourself! Conveniently located near Lackland AFB, SeaWorld, UTSA, and the popular Alamo Ranch Shopping Center. Easy access to Loop 1604, HWY 151, and IH 10. THE WASHER, DRYER, WATER SOFTENER SYSTEM, AND FRIDGE ARE INCLUDED IN THE SALE! Wonderful HOA amenities include an infinity pool, walking trails, a playground, and a lake. PRICE PER SQ FOOT IS EXTREMELY FAVORABLE FOR A NEW BUYER!
